   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-accepting-acceptted" mid="6" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Herbs…?<BR>Could it be... <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, are you poisoned?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-a" mid="8" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I... I was pricked by the Guardian's root in the ancient city.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-b" mid="10" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Oh no. The Guardians in the ancient city are creatures created with alchemy by the past inhabitants of Chiron Island.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-c" mid="12" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>With their masters gone, the Guardians attack anyone who enters the area and their roots are extremely poisonous. It would be fatal for an ordinary human.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-d" mid="14" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What? But I was stabbed! Am I going to die?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-e" mid="16" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Norfe takes a look at your wound)</FONT><BR>Luckily you've been blessed with the protection of several dragons and you also possess half of Red Dragon's jewel so it won't do you much harm.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-f" mid="18" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>But it's still poison so you'll experience some discomfort if left untreated.<BR>When it becomes clear that the herb Geraint is investigating is an antidote, you'd better eat it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-g" mid="20" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Norfe, you seem pretty certain that it is the antidote.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-h" mid="22" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>I don't know why but that's my hunch.<BR>The person could have left behind poisonous herbs, but if the stalker's intention was to kill, there must have been many other chances while following you around.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-i" mid="24" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That means it must be an ally to leave antidotes behind…<BR>Could it be someone sent by Vernicka?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-j" mid="26" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Maybe… But even so, Vernicka would never admit it.<BR>Admitting that he sent someone to follow you would mean that he does not trust us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-k" mid="28" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Hmm... Considering that the only way to Chiron Island is by taking a boat,<BR>maybe the captain at Merca's Port might know something. I heard he's in town now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-l" mid="30" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>And if the herb Geraint is investigating really is an antidote,<BR>it would be better for you to continue the investigation. As long as the stalker is not an enemy, there is no need to delay the investigation.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2" mid="32" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I agree.<BR>I'll go and ask the captain if anyone else has entered Chiron Island.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#662500>Did you say he's in Merca now?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-2" image="QN_Hector.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2-" mid="34" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Ask <FONT color=#a82424>Captain Hector</FONT> if there was anyone else who entered Chiron Island. You might be able to find some useful information.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2257_hector-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Hector.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2257_hector-2-a" mid="36" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Captain Hector$<BR>Hey, good to see you! So how's my boat?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2257_hector-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Hector.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2257_hector-2-b" mid="38" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Captain, was there anyone else who borrowed a boat to Chiron Island?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2257_hector-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Hector.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2257_hector-2-c" mid="40" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Captain Hector$<BR>Hmm? <FONT color=#7e12d2>(The captain pauses a while and replies)</FONT><BR>Everyone knows what kind of Child is ruling Chiron Island. Who else but you guys would be crazy enough to enter that island?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2257_hector-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Hector.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2257_hector-2-d" mid="42" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I was just wondering.<BR>There really wasn't anyone at all? Like someone sent by Vernicka or... I promise I won't tell anyone!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2257_hector-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Hector.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2257_hector-2-e" mid="44" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Captain Hector$<BR>Have you forgotten I'm a citizen of Merca?<BR>I wouldn't tell you for Merca's sake even if there really was such a person. But what I can tell you for sure is that I never received such orders from President Vernicka.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2257_hector-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Hector.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2257_hector-2-f" mid="46" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Wasn't there an awkwardly long pause just now, or is it just me…?)<BR>I see.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2257_hector-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Hector.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2257_hector-3" mid="48" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Captain Hector$<BR>You seem to trust me a lot. <BR>I didn't expect you to ask me such things. Haha!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2257_hector-3" image="QN_Npc_geraint_Kid.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Hector.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2257_hector-3-" mid="50" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Captain Hector$<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Meet Geraint first)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_geraint_Kid.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-3-a" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>You're here at the right time. I've just completed investigating on the herb.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_geraint_Kid.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-3-b" mid="54" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Really? So what is it? </FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_geraint_Kid.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-3-c" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint$<BR>I don't understand why... but the stalker had really left behind an antidote.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_geraint_Kid.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-3-d" mid="58" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2254_geraint-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_geraint_Kid.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2254_geraint-3-!next" mid="60" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Indeed… Norfe was right…</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
